<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.6.5">
<l>āmai yāki yariyāki yaṉṉa māki yantaṇartam</l>
<l>ōma māki yūḻiyā yuvari cūḻnta neṭumpuṇari</l>
<l>cēma matiḷcū ḻilaṅkaikkōṉ ciramuṅ karamun tuṇittumuṉ</l>
<l>kāmaṟ payantāṉ karutumūr kaṇṇa puramnām toḻutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We will worship in Kaṇṇapuram, the city desired by the one</l>
<l rend="indent">who once begot Kāma,</l>
<l>Having become a tortoise, a lion, a swan, having become</l>
<l rend="indent">the priest’s offering and the eons,</l>
<l>Having severed the head and arms of the king of Laṅkā,</l>
<l>Encircled by walls whose defenses are the high waves of the encircling ocean.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
